"""Test the Dictionary Tagger on a simple sentence."""
dt = DictionaryTagger(words=[['Washington'], ['Washington', ',', 'D.C.']])
self.assertEqual([('The', None), ('Washington', 'B-CM'), ('Monument', None),
    ('is', None), ('the', None), ('most', None), ('prominent', None), (
    'structure', None), ('in', None), ('Washington', 'B-CM'), (',', 'I-CM'),
    ('D.C.', 'I-CM')], dt.tag(['The', 'Washington', 'Monument', 'is', 'the',
    'most', 'prominent', 'structure', 'in', 'Washington', ',', 'D.C.']))
